description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 5 Staff Nurses required:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are recruiting! Are you looking for an exciting opportunity?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LOOK NO FURTHER THAN EPSOM AND ST HELIER NHS TRUST!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*CQC RATING- GOOD!* &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for registered nurses to join our very friendly team. We require the applicants to be enthusiastic, motivated and to have good communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Whether you are qualifying in 2020 or an experienced nurse, our teams are looking for you!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Why work for us?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flexible working, which means we can offer shifts to suit you&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Posts available in the acute and/or community setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We can create rotational posts, tailored to you&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fantastic staff benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CapitalNurse Quality Mark for Preceptorship in line with the CapitalNurse programme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We will offer opportunities for you to enhance your clinical skills and will provide support and encouragement to enable you to develop and achieve your full potential.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At ESTH we are committed to acknowledging and building on our successes to ensure we give the best care we can to our patients every day. Our staff wanted more than a set of tools to help support them to do this - they wanted a cultural way of doing things here at ESTH. We have therefore recently launched IDEAS, which is our unique QI programme at Epsom and St Helier.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful candidates will have a genuine desire to become a part of our amazing team and provide outstanding care for our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So if you’re the kind of person who cares about getting things right and wants to make a difference in a forward thinking team we would love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameJulia ArkellJob titleLead Nurse for Recruitment and RetentionEmail addressjulia.arkell@nhs.netTelephone number07500 101088Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Julia Arkell - Lead Nurse for Recruitment and Retention&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;julia.arkell@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
